<TITLE> CEC rallies his troops </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Aug 3 (bdnews24.com)Chief election commissioner ATM Shamsul Huda told his field-level officers on Monday to fulfil their duties without political fear or favour. "The Election Commission is an independent body, and its officials are not liable to anyone other than the commission," said Huda at the start of a training workshop for EC officials at National Economic Council auditorium. Ninety-two newly appointed upazila election officers were among those attending the workshop. "Your personal and political biases should never be reflected in your work," said Huda. He told the field officers to use their training intelligently, and this would be recognised in future evaluations and promotions. Election commissioners Mohammad Sohul Hussein and M Sakhawat Hussain also attended the event. bd
